ComicInfo.Summary: *"Tangled" starring Spittle-Man* Comic gimmicks are brought to the fore as a crazed baby duck seeks Spittle-Man for a battle. *"Super Villain Dating Game"* Three eligible villains try to get lucky with Trixie Larue. *"Hazards of Being a Super Hero"* Various situations in which being awesome can be a real drag. *"Jurassic Classic" starring Milk and Cookies* Milk tries to save America's classic teen from tooth decay. *"Brain Games" starring the Visionary and the Scarlet Itch* The Visionary needs a new brain. Fortunately, the mall is a great place to get a new one. *"Forbush, P.I."* Forbush must find out who's trying to kill him before he gets killed.
